// Toast
// Single notification card with icon, title, optional message, and dismiss button.
// Styled by type: info (blue), success (green), warning (amber), error (red).

InfoIcon, SuccessIcon, WarningIcon, ErrorIcon, CloseIcon are small stateless
SVG icon components used within the toast.

FUNCTION Toast(toast, onDismiss) -> JSX                                EXPORT
  Selects container, icon color, title color, and message color based on
  toast.type.
  Renders icon + title + optional message + dismiss button.
  handleDismiss calls onDismiss(toast.id).

---

FUNCTION getTypeStyles() -> object
  Maps toast.type to Tailwind class strings for container/icon/title/message.
  Defaults to info (blue) for unknown types.

---

FUNCTION getIcon() -> JSX
  Returns the appropriate icon component for toast.type.

---

FUNCTION handleDismiss() -> void
  Calls onDismiss(toast.id).
